Here we need to deal with several questions: 1. Stock maket open at 9 am and close at 4 pm 2. At the open time, stock market record the XX:30, which is not consistent with sentimennt XX::00 3. At close time, stock market also record some stock price

Separate the dataframe into close data_frame and open data_frame
